  "detailed_description": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1212710/extras/619242c0de22392318aa63ede1f1cf08.poster.avif?t=1732985691\" width=480 height=96 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1212710/extras/619242c0de22392318aa63ede1f1cf08.webm?t=1732985691\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1212710/extras/619242c0de22392318aa63ede1f1cf08.mp4?t=1732985691\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >DESCRIPTION</h2><strong>Divine Legacy</strong> is a dark story/character-driven action RPG with hints of humor, friendship, and bonds. Fight your way through hordes of demons, and move one step closer towards the truth!<br><br><i>The god of the damned declared war to the celestial kingdom and the human realm suffer its consequences. In a world where all hope is lost, a hero seeks to make things right once again, but he's only human...</i> <strong>Or is he?</strong><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1212710/extras/fed9d3d07894673ea59255e166da8ffb.poster.avif?t=1732985691\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1212710/extras/fed9d3d07894673ea59255e166da8ffb.webm?t=1732985691\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1212710/extras/fed9d3d07894673ea59255e166da8ffb.mp4?t=1732985691\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >FEATURES</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>About 10 hours of story content<br></li><li>Detailed and lively graphics<br></li><li>Intense real-time action combat system<br></li><li>5 playable characters, each with a different and unique combat style<br></li><li>Extra concept artworks<br></li><li>Hidden collectibles<br></li><li>Over 40 achievements<br></li><li>Extra post-story content<br></li><li>Extra, optional cutscenes and hidden dialogues<br></li><li>Secret unlockable content</li></ul>",
